My Topic Is Destiny 2
Destiny 2 is a First Person Looter/Shooter video game developed by Bungie Studios and was released in 2017. It has an amazing campaign, lore, PvP(Player vs Player) and is an online only game, meaning you have to have an internet connection to even play.
My love for Destiny began when a friend introduced me to the game, already a huge fan of the Halo series also developed by Bungie Studios I knew destiny was going to be an incredible game from the beginning.
By: Tony Power
